articles.title: Australia to hold federal election on 3 May - BBC.com
articles.description: Prime Minister Anthony Albanese will be seeking to fight off a resurgent opposition and win a second term.
articles.content:
Tiffanie Turnbull
Australia will head to the polls for a federal election on 3 May.
